// JoinSquadSection component - Call to action for joining the team
---

<section
  class="h-svh bg-purple-300 flex px-64 gap-16 justify-center items-center relative"
>
  <div class="w-full">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-8xl font-normal text-white split">
        Join onze <br /> Squad!
      </h1>
      <button
        class="group relative mt-8 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 via-pink-600 to-purple-800 px-8 py-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-white shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-purple-500/25 focus:outline-none focus:ring-4 focus:ring-purple-500/50 active:scale-95"
      >
